code: import axios from"axios";var REACT_APP_BASE_URL=process.env.REACT_APP_BASE_URL;export var ResetPass=function ResetPass(user){return new Promise(function(resolve,reject){var data=user;axios.post(REACT_APP_BASE_URL+"/forgetpassword",data).then(function(res){resolve(res);}).catch(function(error){reject(error);});});};
